race.comment: IMPERIAL FORCE (9) gave weight to ZEALOUSLY first-up, before fading late when twelfth to Linebacker over 1300m in the G3 Silver Eagle at this track. Gets a much better set-up today and assess on his narrow second in the G2 Arrowfield over 1200m last April. Value chance. SHEZANALISTER (12) never a threat from the poor draw when last in the G3 Sydney Stakes at this track. Fitter now and will find this more to her liking despite coming up with a wide marble again. Place prospects best. ACCREDITED (5) resumes for the in form Pride yard with a solid fresh record. Fitted with the one solid 805m trial and gets his chance from the low draw. ROMEO'S CHOICE (10) tough gelding who returns from a let-up. Proven at this course and distance and has a good heavy track record. Value chance.
